To remove the 404 error in the following command

Sudo apt-get update 

Follow the below steps

1) Go to search type "Update-Manager"

2) Select Ubuntu Software Tab

3) Select other server option from server selection box

3 a) From the list of servers available click "SELECT BEST SERVER OPTION"

4) Click Ok

Optional

5) Go to other software tab,
 
  5a)  Check whether all the options are ticked
  
6) Finally click close

On clicking close check whether the updating cache dialog box appears!!
